Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎很冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把被炉拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定要拿出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…放在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉  被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械皇女克拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能来太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  驱魔本来就是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的有妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是梨香当时吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没什么东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨香  会不会是你学习过度太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情节几乎已经成规定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了  喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来点上次的仙贝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那张脸总觉得在哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就从冰箱里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  喝点茶暖暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度测定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华氏104.6度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成分分析完成还有55秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么叫不知道  真田小姐是巴鲁哈拉星的侍女长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在八大皇家里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下也几乎不在别人面前露面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这样的人连见她都受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确连我们皇女在国中也几乎碰不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  说难以理解也好不可思议也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我解释一下这一连串的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打扰十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,necomimi@tokinoyu…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地址是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信件  有信件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您告诉我那个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话会很长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…那个…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  请别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  节省时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不节省时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就直接说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们拉到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样  什么不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然是巴鲁哈拉星的皇女之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是机械
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的羽翼和大家不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是巴鲁哈拉皇家的最高机密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来的我小时候就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体的事情我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的记忆都是被制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:07:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所知  八位皇女是巴鲁哈拉星权力的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何一位都不能缺少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以制造了我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且移植了去世的皇女的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于自己的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个虚伪的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十天前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认了我的设计上有致命的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离不可维护的动力炉停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这个计数器显示到0的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁哈拉第一的期待之星莱妮殿下登场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家原来在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兜遍整个街区了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可是新买的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让大家快点欣赏一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道克拉斯是机械人的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械人？  克拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事摆明了是胡扯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  都是你说是胡扯什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我在说谎罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你平时表现就是难以信任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下  请振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位别给她骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是个坏孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（伊拉伊萨：某超喜欢恶作剧的角色，不是My fair lady里的那个……）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是伊拉伊萨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你闭嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些冷漠的言语使我的少女驱动产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女驱动？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  模仿人的内心使自己痛苦的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是人  明明不是真的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请求和人先生一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有三天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在这期间拥有美好的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我的少女驱动满足的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和理想的男友梦幻般的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瓦露克蕾的结婚仪式上第一次见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好羡慕瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和这么好的人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有想抢走你的他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有别的人可以拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  和小克约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  和人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只想沉浸在这份愉悦中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明白这只是回路里的电流信号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是第二天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下那么的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始你就在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在调查阻止动力炉停止的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…得充电了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能做这样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是机械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的颜色  清淡的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是地球上的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能带着这份记忆消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已别无所求了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到地球太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位都在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在晃来晃去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小子还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还和我的和人先生如此的有气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱妮殿下  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（音羽：这个不知道出处……）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是音羽先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  看样子时间已到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人先生  诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露克蕾  要和和人先生永远恩爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要连我的份也一起幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  一定有什么办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机能停止还有120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机能停止还有90秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐冷却的热流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请重新燃起生命之火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流遍钢铁的身躯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入最终倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10…9…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点想点办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4…3…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹  这是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信奇迹  思念会传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是瓦露克蕾的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  克拉斯是机械的事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都说了是胡扯的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心真的是机械的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（波库：某穿青蛙衣的奇怪生物）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  波库
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波库是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  波库…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙以前就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直和她是同学所以知道的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一开始就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你平时乱说话搞得别人信不过你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是收到别的什么电波了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现问题  请重新启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有保存的程序全部会被清除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  就是刚刚的角度  海多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家真是够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么巴鲁哈拉的人都是些怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能我道歉也没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候起就被她烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己是机器人  宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人也没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之她就是这么不知所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得比起克拉斯真的死了现在这样好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露也希望小克活着好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下  您多善良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克  已经到巴鲁哈拉星了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回去了也算松口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的一点没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你也给我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次什么时候才能再见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  明天的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这时代了她居然还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短期的房租
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都霸占了别人的房间了  能不能别再自说自话的烧水了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  克拉斯殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您藏身藏的太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达沸点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华氏212度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是海多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯那个样子真的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为巴鲁哈拉皇家也不愿意说起克拉斯的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高机密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周还要厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  电波皇女克拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备哦

